<h2 style="margin-bottom:1.75rem">Our Fundraising Progress</h2>

<p style="max-width:700px; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto">
  <sl-progress-bar value="0" animate-to-value="{{ funding.percentage }}" style="--height:40px; --indicator-color:var(--color-medium-green)">
    <strong style="font-size:150%">${{ funding.current }}</strong>
  </sl-progress-bar>
</p>

<h3 style="color:rgb(var(--sl-color-neutral-500))">
  Goal: <ui-label style="color:var(--color-orange); letter-spacing:0.02em; text-shadow:2px 2px 2px var(--color-brick)">${{ funding.goal | string | replace: '000', ',000'}}</ui-label>
</h3>

<p style="margin-top:3rem;text-align:center;font-size:110%">
  <strong>March 2022 Update:</strong> <br/>
  The fundraiser has successfully concluded! <a href="https://www.bridgetownrb.com">Check out the new Bridgetown 1.0 release today!</a> And if you'd still like to contribute to Bridgetown financially, the <a href="https://github.com/sponsors/jaredcwhite">GitHub Sponsors program</a> is alive and well. Thank you to everyone who helped make this dream a reality!
</p>

